  "title": "Care Support Associate ( HCA /  BCA / CSA) WEST #HYT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Jurong East Govt<br>\n<strong>Pay:</strong> $13 per hour (with CPF) / Direct Perm Up to $2.5K</p>\n<p><br>\n<strong>Contract Duration:</strong> 6 months (with the potential for permanent conversion)<br>\n<strong>Schedule:</strong> 5 days per week, with AM and PM shifts (42 hours/week)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide essential nursing care to patients, assisting with daily activities and transfers.</li>\n  <li>Perform basic housekeeping duties as required.</li>\n  <li>Ensure patient comfort and safety during care activities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>HMI certification / BCA / HCA work experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All qualified applicants, please<strong> click “ APPLY NOW”</strong></p>\n<p>Or you may send in your resume to:</p>\n<p><strong>Whatsapp: </strong><u><strong>https://wa.me/+6597430026</strong></u></p>\n<p><strong>Email : </strong><a href=\"mailto:kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg\"><u><strong>kimlow@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></a></p>\n<p>Kimmy Low Yi Ting (Kim) | CEI Registration Number: R23112122</p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA LICENCE Number: 99C4599</p>",
